<COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Bush</COREF> has called for an agreement by next September at the latest .
But some American defense officials believe <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">the North Atlantic Treaty Organization</COREF> should take more time to examine the long - term implications of the options being considered .
