<COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">France , Britain and Italy</COREF> all have light tanks <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> would like to keep out of <COREF ID="17" TYPE="IDENT">the talks</COREF> .
