Defining combat aircraft is even tougher .
<COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">The Soviets</COREF> insisted that aircraft be brought into <COREF ID="17" TYPE="IDENT">the talks</COREF> , then argued for exempting <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">some 4,000 Russian planes</COREF> because <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> are `` solely defensive . ''
