Accounting problems raise more knotty issues .
<COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">Greece and Turkey</COREF> , for example , are suspected of overstating <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> arsenals in hopes that <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> can emerge from the arms - reduction treaty with large remaining forces to deter <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT">each other</COREF> .
